description:
Please help me fill in the blanks in the table; cells marked "-" do not need to be filled.
After filling in the table, please draw a trend chart in chronological order. Requirements:
Years shall be in increasing order from left to right;
The height of coordinate points shall be consistent with the weight relationship;
The color of coordinate points shall be drawn according to the provided color card. The more blue the color, the lower the device computing power; the more red the color, the higher the device computing power. Devices with computing power lower than 100,000 addition operations per second shall be blue, and the rest shall be red;
The vicinity of each coordinate point shall be labeled with: device name, device weight, and device picture.
